node.text:
There’s a lot to unpack here. 

First, for ME to be the voice that’s heard when it’s the only time IN THE ENTIRE MOVIE we hear Tom speak words. What the H bro. I’m honored. Ironically I don’t have the words to describe this feeling 😂 

Second, getting back together with @preachbal4 for him to murder these keys was a pleasure, especially after the film’s music department said they had a ton of players ready to go but I’m glad I declined because nobody does it like @preachbal4 and myself 

Third. The history I have as a @tomandjerry fan goes so far back you’d have to carbon date that shit. 

Fourth. The fact that they kept my natural voice at the beginning after they said they wanted the whole thing “super robotic” let’s me know they actually listened to my opinion (which is super rare for a giant film studio) so @wbpictures thank you guys

Fifth. To have @comedianlilrel as Tom’s conscience and one of his lines was “we just kinda look alike” almost took me out 😂 

I don’t have a sixth but I am trying to write this through tears and I just wanna thank my whole team and everybody involved that made this happen

@tomandjerry movie out now in theaters and @hbomax

node.text: I’m not in this position because I followed trends. Everybody has their #Top5 and you can easily have your own if you stop giving a shit about what ppl think of you and start giving a shit about what YOU think. You have a chance to swerve into the empty lane. It’s gonna add a little time to your trip but there won’t be any traffic in your way because everybody else is still trying to take the same exit. #DoSomethingElse
